{"tid":362561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攀欄替模特兒拍照　健美先生商廈失足墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-08-17T04:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T15:23:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":128,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be61ab5a8cc986c1a108c7e80eba72550b2b3f8c","tid":362561,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"中區利源東街9號利東大廈，早上9時，一名身穿短褲、波鞋、身材健碩男子（約30歲）由大廈高處墮下，跌落4樓平台重傷昏迷，其同事見狀立即報案，救護員趕至，證實事主明顯死亡，地上留下一攤血漬。 <br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，初步獲悉死者在該大廈工作，熱愛健身，曾參加健美比賽，榮獲健美先生美譽。現場消息稱，事發時，他在12樓替一對model情侶拍照，並曾在Fb打卡，惟期間疑爬到高位取景時，失足墮下，警方正展開調查。"},{"pid":"da5d97edc70b8abc04de4678ddb559aca058d51f","tid":362561,"uid":19552,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"12樓替一對model情侶拍照，並曾在Fb打卡，惟期間疑爬到高位取景時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73889acdd4d2921dcf871707415474b08470b055","tid":362561,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4577f09e7799ceba2853983290df778cda9eb544","tid":362561,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:22:26.000Z","msg":"係咪Mr. Bean 既情節黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73452b98fb8e7696f35bf456e42e07b330bab8fa","tid":362561,"uid":19552,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d08xTHX.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd08xTHX.jpg%3F1&h=c8d9c376&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e2d71b3dc3e1154aee4b88f09fd527cf58f6592","tid":362561,"uid":3976,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"點解我會睇錯左蔡欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ddf088c386528080e177b50150df559b4cf4cc","tid":362561,"uid":106340,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:24:18