.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F123925_a03db05fef3a3c5bc6bf756f3be7fbdb.jpg&h=aa6b605a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n等睇有人追討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為追夢喪命 死了也風流"},{"pid":"9ff20039b5cb17a5e65171b5312a2cc9f21aa695","tid":362561,"uid":26451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba9b9d9b814907cc7be2fdc77982a19916c43451","tid":362561,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d08xTHX.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd08xTHX.jpg%3F1&h=c8d9c376&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n博盡無悔好撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575e0f38e0b3487e4adb3c76022e7efca6b43ce1","tid":362561,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"死者姓江26歲，英文名阿Will，在墮樓大廈內一間健身中心做健身教練。《蘋果》聯絡到樓上另一間健身中心的黃姓職員，同時也是死者的舊同事。黃今早返工，已經發生墮樓事件，他向大廈保安員了解後，得悉死者竟然就是阿Will，感到非常突然。黃估計是意外：「自殺唔會，估計是意外，可能佢影相，響12樓平台爬出去，外面空間好窄㗎！」他估計事主失足墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n黃指，阿Will年約25歲，是freelance健身教練，本身有參加健美比賽，前兩日剛於澳門一項健美比賽中獲獎。黃形容，阿Will「有上進心、好nice」，由於他不時自拍上載到交友網站，黃估計他今次也是在12樓平台自拍時出意外。「嗰度有差唔多5呎多的欄杆，爬出去，外面空間好窄。」<br />\n<br />\n他在互聯網上自我介紹稱，有4年個人健身教練經驗，剛於前兩日，在GLOBAL CLASSIC澳門站邀請賽獲第4名，另外於2016奧林匹克先生亞洲香港賽獲亞軍、2016香港健美健身總會男子型體健美錦標賽第六名。他的fb內亦滿載健身比賽及生活照，其中一張合成相片顯示，他在2010年皮膚白滑，經過艱苦的操練，2016年即展現8件腹肌的健美身型。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他在學歷簡介中指出，中學於深水灣的南島中學畢業，再先後於清華大學商業/管理經濟學及英國曼徹斯特大學工商管理畢業。2013年起投身健身教練行列。"},{"pid":"4621871d460711a97668d13816f6241d259d0755","tid":362561,"uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502943647_45a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502943647_45a1.jpg&h=aa6d0e5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f47f172fc8ddc27bbb2d81e9ab5d13a8116ecbd2","tid":362561,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"博盡無悔"},{"pid":"fecf697af51075bb9bcdbbd55236a0582b5d8a70","tid":362561,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502943647_45a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502943647_45a1.jpg&h=aa6d0e5c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea361b0d311e4a7a7f89b22ff7aafed6ffeca254","tid":362561,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502944025_ad91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502944025_ad91.jpg&h=7b45a358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8581b25638dbd918281275d58595d7ab567d29ec","tid":362561,"uid":3457,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"健身教練 都係畜生黎 死得好"},{"pid":"0e557d8fd9b95582ccf24d3b2edcfafb790b19fe","tid":362561,"uid":1818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"係咪香港第一單影rooftop死既人"},{"pid":"e54e9622f8b075447cc29f8076edaeb129798256","tid":362561,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:59:28.00